About - Roblox Academy

What is Roblox Academy?

Roblox Academy was first started in 2018 of Summer. Roblox Academy owner, joshuadl12 started the group. Then, the Dev Crew came along. Roblox Academy as well as Roblox Academy Offices was opened for Pre-Alpha testing. A few months later, RBXAcademy Admin. Head development is joshuadl12. You can message us via email at rbx2academy@gmail.com or via contact form at the bottom
